================================================================================
                 SECTION 5: ETHICAL USE RESTRICTIONS (ABSOLUTE)
================================================================================

The use of this Software is STRICTLY PROHIBITED for:

   a) GENETIC USE RESTRICTION TECHNOLOGIES (GURTs): Any breeding activity
      involving technologies that render seeds sterile, non-viable, or
      dependent on proprietary chemical inducers
   
   b) TERMINATOR TECHNOLOGY: Any technology that produces sterile seeds,
      preventing farmers from saving and replanting seeds
   
   c) TRAITOR TECHNOLOGY: Any technology requiring chemical application
      to activate or maintain genetic traits in plants
   
   d) SEED TERMINATION: Any method that prevents seeds from being saved,
      replanted, or used for subsequent generations

This prohibition is ABSOLUTE and admits NO EXCEPTIONS. Violation results
in immediate and automatic termination of all license rights, including
any Commercial License.

For complete ethical use terms, see ETHICAL_USE_POLICY.md which is
incorporated herein by reference.

